s.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180306%2Fs00001%2F1520246982944&h=303215d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180306/s00001/1520246982944</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"究竟係我錯覺定點<br />\n覺得個&ldquo;搶&rdquo;字用得好奇怪<br />\n唔係用個&ldquo;赴&rdquo;字正常啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"匪語文法你識條毛"},{"pid":"b7d671ec602a7ea8fb51da891778bd160cc99882","tid":582820,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ac5adb03c5088327aff287598047ac2be041901","tid":582820,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23638bf49d13e33f1cf2499bbfc0601d8a434650","tid":582820,"uid":139484,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c071edeab2e5101a05aa5a72445e5383625438ec","tid":582820,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180306/s00001/cec5704597df2bd3d42bcef20782b8fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180306%2Fs00001%2Fcec5704597df2bd3d42bcef20782b8fd.jpg&h=1710e2b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創作比賽最忌抄襲。有網民路過一間小學時，從校門外橫額看到區內道路及交通安全小學標語創作比賽得獎作品，因句式不常見，加上不似出自小學生，遂上網查看，結果竟發現「寧繞百步遠，不搶一步險」一句，實為兩岸常見用於交通安全的標語，早於2011年起內地網站出現。<br />\n<br />\n內地公安常以此為口號，其中南京鐵路公安，去年曾在微博上載有關標語照片，呼籲民眾小心過路。<br />\n<br />\n橫額資料顯示，比賽由大埔區小學校長會主辦、大埔區議會贊助。部分網民認為，有關情況不應姑息。有人直指會向大會及校方了解，希望讓孩子明白創作絕不可抄襲之理。亦有網民認為教導孩子的同時，也不宜過分施壓，以免對他們產生負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n大埔區小學校長會主席冼儉偉表示，今早已得悉事件，將會了解和跟進，再和校長會探討比賽流程和章程改善空間。冼儉偉說他不是比賽評審，但透露一般標語創作比賽中，都會先遮蓋校名，再讓評審評分。<br />\n<br />\n獲獎學生所屬學校校長表示，昨日得悉事件，已即時除下印有獲獎標語的橫額。校長直言為事件感到痛心，因學生創作標語涉及抄襲。目前她仍未跟學生討論事件，因現時是考試周，不希望影響學生，之後將通知學生和家長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180306/s00001/1520246982944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180306%2Fs00001%2F1520246982944&d=FkRYAJ%2BVlyd61e66YX%2B9U26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5c2a7bdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180306%2Fs00001%2F1520246982944&h=303215d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180306/s00001/1520246982944</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"究竟係我錯覺定點<br />\n覺得個&ldquo;搶&rdquo;字用得好奇怪<br />\n唔係用個&ldquo;赴&rdquo;字正常啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"匪語文法你識條毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:06:51.000Z","msg":"同埋好多時呢D標語成日都會犯一個嚴重錯誤,就係佢地好鐘意前句後句相同位置都用返同一個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678f500e9f6997e96b654031e18cbce58eeb7e17","tid":582820,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:08:14.000Z","msg":"00後支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593af20d03f55c58b0fb5322ef767ab5b58aff30","tid":582820,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"如果比我改,我起碼要改走後句個步字:寧繞百步遠,不搶一分險"},{"pid":"8aa9354c78650a4c3568c9004478407d422cbe47","tid":582820,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:09:31.000Z","msg":"成句要用普通話讀"},{"pid":"05b53f4d72de0ce902142c92cd3ebeaee20f42fc","tid":582820,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"跑步，同游水咪又抄人，抗議無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da480e9e8b4f35fbf3ea8740e00eae7d3a4a424f","tid":582820,"uid":59312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"呢